63
00:04:56,059 --> 00:04:57,100
Tidak.

64
00:04:59,970 --> 00:05:01,069
Tidak.

65
00:05:03,470 --> 00:05:04,800
Tidak mungkin.

66
00:05:35,170 --> 00:05:37,499
Begitu melihatmu saat aku masuk

67
