85
00:06:36,329 --> 00:06:38,199
Dahulu kamu benar-benar mencintaiku?

86
00:06:47,410 --> 00:06:48,770
Itu sudah cukup.

87
00:06:50,079 --> 00:06:51,139
Ini.

88
00:06:57,780 --> 00:07:00,389
"Kontrak"

89
